About  PPMA






  











Welcome to PPM America
What We Do*
At PPM America, asset management is our sole focus. We  manage approximately $108 billion in assets for our clients, and our mission is  clear-cut – to produce superior investment results for them. This goal  recognizes that, as an active manager, the value we provide to our clients rests  on our ability to outperform. In order to do so, we invest heavily in our  people, infrastructure and idea generation while staying focused on what’s important to our clients.
Who We Are*
Highly Experienced and Collaborative: Our investment professionals have on average over 16 years of investment experience and 12 years of tenure at PPMA. Their collective expertise is strengthened by a team-based approach to idea generation.
Value-Disciplined: We operate with an unwavering commitment to our core  corporate values as well as to a relative value based investment approach.
Research-Driven: In our industry, taking risk is necessary to succeed. We rely heavily on research to make sure risks are well measured, consistent with our investment philosophy and in line with clients’ goals.
 




Firm  Overview


Clients





We  are a large US-based asset manager and part of one of the world’s leading  financial services organizations.


Our asset base reflects a wide range of client and portfolio types.











Capabilities 


Investment Approach





We manage strategies spanning the fixed income, public  equity, private equity and commercial real estate-related markets. 


Our  belief that markets are inherently inefficient over the short run drives our  investment approach.







 


* As of 31 December 2016. Includes assets of PPM Finance Inc., an affiliate that manages assets that are not securities, such as commercial mortgage loans and certain real estate investments. As of 30 June 2016, PPM America managed approximately $101 billion.



