PPMA - Market Outlook







  











Macro Update
Lower long-term interest rates, a weaker US dollar and lower oil prices – these price trends have run counter to expectations entering 2017, but have been driven by a macro environment dominated by changing central bank policy and expectations around global economic growth and the Trump administration.




 

