            PPM America and its affiliates provide investment advisory services to a variety of portfolio product types originated by affiliates of its United Kingdom parent, including Jackson National Life in the United States, and a number of UK and Asian affiliates. PPM also provides services to other affiliated and unaffiliated institutional clients, including collateralized debt obligations, private investment funds, institutional accounts and mutual funds. PPM invests in areas such as public and private fixed income, public equity, real estate related assets and private equity. PPM America is an indirect subsidiary of Prudential, a publicly traded holding company. It provides insurance and financial services directly and through its subsidiaries and affiliates throughout the world.
          






















