PPMA - Overview






  









 


Firm Overview
Our Group*
PPM  America, Inc. (“PPMA”) is an indirect, wholly owned subsidiary of Prudential  plc** (our “UK Parent” or "Parent"), an international financial services group (the "Group") with significant  operations in Asia, the US and the UK. The Group has nearly 24 million  insurance customers and approximately $753 billion of assets under management.** While its  reach is global, the Group maintains on-the-ground operations in many of the  markets that it serves, allowing it to customize its service, products and  expertise to the needs of local clients. 
Our Company*
PPMA serves as one of our Group’s US-based asset managers.  We are an SEC-registered investment advisor, and together with our affiliate,  PPM Finance, Inc., have expertise across a range of fixed income, public and  private equity, and commercial real estate-related asset classes.
We were founded in 1990 to manage institutional accounts for  our corporate affiliates, including Jackson National Life  Insurance Company® (“Jackson®”).  Since then, we have expanded our capabilities  and client reach in a disciplined manner while maintaining the same level of  detailed analysis and risk management that has been critical to successfully  serving Jackson. We manage approximately $108 billion for internal,  institutional and retail mandates worldwide. 
  
* As of 31 December 2016. Includes assets of PPM Finance Inc., an affiliate that  manages assets that are not securities, such as commercial mortgage loans and  certain real estate investments. As of 31 December 2016, PPM America managed  approximately $101 billion.
** As of 30 June 2016. Our UK Parent is incorporated in and has its principal place of business in England. With its affiliated companies it constitutes one of the world's leading financial services groups and has been in existence for over 165 years. It provides insurance and financial services directly and through its subsidiaries and affiliates throughout the world. Our UK Parent is not affiliated in any manner with Prudential Financial, Inc., a company whose principal place of business is in the United States of America.
*** Towers Watson, “The 500 largest asset managers” November 2015. Size for ranking includes assets of our UK Parent and each of its affiliates. 






PPMA Quick Facts*
Headquartered in Chicago, IL
Part of financial services group ranked 25th globally for AUM***
