PPM America, Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to other pooled investment vehicles and corporations. PPM America was founded in 1990 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with additional offices in Schaumburg, Illinois… MorePPM America, Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to other pooled investment vehicles and corporations. PPM America was founded in 1990 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with additional offices in Schaumburg, Illinois and New York, New York. It operates as a subsidiary of Jackson National Life Insurance Company
At PPM Americas, the lean Information Technology department operates out of the company’s Chicago, IL corporate headquarters. The department focuses investment support systems and applications.

The IT Networks division deploys and maintains network services, manages hardware and software from initial specification… MoreAt PPM Americas, the lean Information Technology department operates out of the company’s Chicago, IL corporate headquarters. The department focuses investment support systems and applications.

The IT Networks division deploys and maintains network services, manages hardware and software from initial specification through decommissioning, and supports users. The team also manages networks and servers, installs and upgrades hardware and software support users, and troubleshoots hardware and software.

Consultants are tasked with most software development projects. 





