About PPM America, Inc.
PPM America is an asset manager that provides investment services for a variety of institutional mandates and retail products sourced primarily from affiliates in the US, UK, and Asia. PPM America's expertise spans across a wide range of fixed-income and equity asset classes, with an emphasis on fundamental company and security research.


What employees say
“I am given the opportunity and autonomy to perform.”
“I have the opportunity to work on new technology and lead large scale projects.”
“I love my job because each day presents new challenges and my ideas are always welcome.”

“I work with a great group of people. I am paid extremely well and have a great working relationship with all of the people I work with and for.”
“My work is challenging and fulfilling.”

