PPM America , INC. : Top Money Managers  



















































Welcome to PPMA






  




















Finding Value
To seek outperformance we focus on measuring both fundamentals and relative value. This approach is visible across the asset classes and strategies we manage.









Earning Trust
We earn the trust of clients throughout the world by seeking superior investment results. Each component of our business reflects this goal — our staff, our infrastructure and our processes.









Sharing Our Views
Recent market volatility has resulted in a favorable credit-picking landscape. At the least, fundamentals don't present a significant headwind, and valuations in certain sectors have become more attractive.







